comments: Bogdanovic (UTA) extends his forearm into Evans's (GSW) body and initiates contact that affects his ability to defend.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) sets the screen on O'Neale (UTA) and does not deliver contact.
O'Neale (UTA) jumps and maintains a vertical position while defending Cauley-Stein's (GSW) dunk attempt.
Gobert (UTA) reaches in and makes contact with Lee's (GSW) arm that affects his ability to pass.
Mitchell (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position on Burks (GSW).
Cauley-Stein (GSW) cleanly blocks Ingles's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Robinson III (GSW) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) makes marginal contact with Gobert (UTA) and does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
Mitchell (UTA) and Russell (GSW) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Ingles (UTA) makes marginal contact with Lee (GSW) during his driving shot attempt.
Burks (GSW) and Mitchell (UTA) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Burks (GSW) holds Mitchell (UTA) and affects his FOM.
Video evidence is inconclusive if Russell (GSW) steps out of bounds along the sideline.
Robinson III (GSW) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (UTA).
Robinson III (GSW) makes contact with Bogdanovic's (UTA) head.

Chriss (GSW) establishes his screening position in a wide stance, but the contact with O'Neale (UTA) occurs to his chest.  After Chriss disengages from the screen, he steps backwards and the two players make incidental foot to foot contact.
